        "TileImage": "$($repository fc05b7e0-0900-4b9a-bd57-ea9271d080c7).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47. Devin and Dale are in a love triangle with Brandon, which is causing quite the controversy around the farm. What is less well known, is that this is, in fact, a love quadrilateral. Our client is the unrequited lover of Brandon, who has asked us to put an end to their competition, and to their own will-they-won&apos;t-they love story with Brandon. Let&apos;s put them out of their misery, shall we? I will leave you to prepare. Good luck.",
